{"sections":{"main":{"type":"main-page","blocks":{"heading":{"type":"text","name":"Title","settings":{"text":"<h1>{{ closest.page.title }}<\/h1>","width":"100%","max_width":"normal","alignment":"left","type_preset":"h2","font":"var(--font-primary--family)","font_size":"","line_height":"normal","letter_spacing":"normal","case":"none","wrap":"pretty","color":"","background":false,"background_color":"#00000026","corner_radius":0,"padding-block-start":0,"padding-block-end":0,"padding-inline-start":0,"padding-inline-end":0},"blocks":{}},"page-content":{"type":"page-content","settings":{},"blocks":{}}},"block_order":["heading","page-content"],"disabled":true,"settings":{"content_direction":"column","gap":32,"color_scheme":"","padding-block-start":40,"padding-block-end":80}},"section_76BTfJ":{"type":"section","blocks":{"logo_CrXWXU":{"type":"logo","name":"t:names.logo","settings":{"inverse":false,"font":"heading","unit":"pixel","percent_width":100,"pixel_height":48,"custom_mobile_size":false,"unit_mobile":"percent","percent_width_mobile":100,"pixel_height_mobile":120,"padding-block-start":0,"padding-block-end":0,"padding-inline-start":0,"padding-inline-end":0},"blocks":{}},"text_mVPQHV":{"type":"text","name":"t:names.heading","settings":{"text":"<h3><strong>Pourquoi certains chiens vivent mal certaines situations du quotidien<\/strong><\/h3>","width":"100%","max_width":"none","alignment":"left","type_preset":"rte","font":"var(--font-body--family)","font_size":"1rem","line_height":"normal","letter_spacing":"normal","case":"none","wrap":"pretty","color":"var(--color-foreground)","background":false,"background_color":"#00000026","corner_radius":0,"padding-block-start":0,"padding-block-end":0,"padding-inline-start":0,"padding-inline-end":0},"blocks":{}},"text_QDNkLK":{"type":"text","name":"t:names.text","settings":{"text":"<p>Aboiements liés au stress, difficultés à rester seul à la maison, trajets, visites chez le vétérinaire, changements d’habitude ou bruits soudains comme les orages et les feux d’artifice… certains chiens ont plus de mal que d’autres à gérer ces moments. Ces réactions sont souvent liées à l’anxiété, à la peur ou à une difficulté à retrouver un état de calme.<\/p>","width":"100%","max_width":"none","alignment":"left","type_preset":"rte","font":"var(--font-body--family)","font_size":"1rem","line_height":"normal","letter_spacing":"normal","case":"none","wrap":"pretty","color":"var(--color-foreground)","background":false,"background_color":"#00000026","corner_radius":0,"padding-block-start":0,"padding-block-end":0,"padding-inline-start":0,"padding-inline-end":0},"blocks":{}},"text_UjL3BP":{"type":"text","name":"t:names.heading","settings":{"text":"<h3><strong>Le principe de la pression douce<\/strong><\/h3>","width":"fit-content","max_width":"none","alignment":"left","type_preset":"rte","font":"var(--font-body--family)","font_size":"1rem","line_height":"normal","letter_spacing":"normal","case":"none","wrap":"pretty","color":"var(--color-foreground)","background":false,"background_color":"#00000026","corner_radius":0,"padding-block-start":0,"padding-block-end":0,"padding-inline-start":0,"padding-inline-end":0},"blocks":{}},"text_HeEhzN":{"type":"text","name":"t:names.text","settings":{"text":"<p>Serenimo s’inspire du principe de <strong>pression douce et constante<\/strong>, souvent comparé à la sensation d’être contenu ou enveloppé de manière rassurante. L’idée est d’offrir au chien un repère physique simple, qui peut l’aider à se sentir davantage sécurisé dans certaines situations stressantes.<\/p>","width":"fit-content","max_width":"none","alignment":"left","type_preset":"rte","font":"var(--font-body--family)","font_size":"1rem","line_height":"normal","letter_spacing":"normal","case":"none","wrap":"pretty","color":"var(--color-foreground)","background":false,"background_color":"#00000026","corner_radius":0,"padding-block-start":0,"padding-block-end":0,"padding-inline-start":0,"padding-inline-end":0},"blocks":{}},"text_kmX33q":{"type":"text","name":"t:names.heading","settings":{"text":"<p><strong>Dans quels cas Serenimo peut être utile<\/strong><\/p>","width":"fit-content","max_width":"none","alignment":"left","type_preset":"h3","font":"var(--font-body--family)","font_size":"1rem","line_height":"normal","letter_spacing":"normal","case":"none","wrap":"pretty","color":"var(--color-foreground)","background":false,"background_color":"#00000026","corner_radius":0,"padding-block-start":0,"padding-block-end":0,"padding-inline-start":0,"padding-inline-end":0},"blocks":{}},"text_qeKfx4":{"type":"text","name":"t:names.text","settings":{"text":"<p>Serenimo peut être utilisé dans plusieurs moments sensibles du quotidien, notamment lorsque le chien :<\/p><ul><li>aboie sous l’effet du stress<\/li><li>supporte mal l’absence de son maître<\/li><li>se montre inquiet en voiture ou lors d’une visite chez le vétérinaire<\/li><li>réagit fortement aux bruits comme les orages ou les feux d’artifice<\/li><li>a besoin d’un cadre rassurant pendant certains apprentissages ou changements de routine.<\/li><\/ul>","width":"fit-content","max_width":"none","alignment":"left","type_preset":"rte","font":"var(--font-body--family)","font_size":"1rem","line_height":"normal","letter_spacing":"normal","case":"none","wrap":"pretty","color":"var(--color-foreground)","background":false,"background_color":"#00000026","corner_radius":0,"padding-block-start":0,"padding-block-end":0,"padding-inline-start":0,"padding-inline-end":0},"blocks":{}},"text_ejBDFi":{"type":"text","name":"t:names.heading","settings":{"text":"<p><strong>Une aide simple à intégrer à la routine<\/strong><\/p>","width":"fit-content","max_width":"normal","alignment":"left","type_preset":"h3","font":"var(--font-body--family)","font_size":"1rem","line_height":"normal","letter_spacing":"normal","case":"none","wrap":"pretty","color":"var(--color-foreground)","background":false,"background_color":"#00000026","corner_radius":0,"padding-block-start":0,"padding-block-end":0,"padding-inline-start":0,"padding-inline-end":0},"blocks":{}},"text_kBc3rF":{"type":"text","name":"t:names.text","settings":{"text":"<p>L’un des intérêts de ce type de gilet est aussi sa simplicité d’utilisation. Les sources consultées recommandent généralement de l’introduire progressivement, dans un moment calme, puis de le mettre quelques minutes avant la situation sensible afin d’aider le chien à mieux vivre l’événement. <\/p>","width":"fit-content","max_width":"none","alignment":"left","type_preset":"rte","font":"var(--font-body--family)","font_size":"1rem","line_height":"normal","letter_spacing":"normal","case":"none","wrap":"pretty","color":"var(--color-foreground)","background":false,"background_color":"#00000026","corner_radius":0,"padding-block-start":0,"padding-block-end":0,"padding-inline-start":0,"padding-inline-end":0},"blocks":{}},"text_EArqjb":{"type":"text","name":"t:names.heading","settings":{"text":"<p><strong>Un accompagnement, pas une solution magique<\/strong><\/p>","width":"fit-content","max_width":"normal","alignment":"left","type_preset":"h3","font":"var(--font-body--family)","font_size":"1rem","line_height":"normal","letter_spacing":"normal","case":"none","wrap":"pretty","color":"var(--color-foreground)","background":false,"background_color":"#00000026","corner_radius":0,"padding-block-start":0,"padding-block-end":0,"padding-inline-start":0,"padding-inline-end":0},"blocks":{}},"text_PK7paa":{"type":"text","name":"t:names.text","settings":{"text":"<p>Chaque chien réagit différemment. Serenimo n’a pas vocation à tout remplacer, mais à offrir une aide supplémentaire, douce et rassurante, dans les moments où ton chien a besoin d’être accompagné avec plus de sérénité. Cette approche rejoint le positionnement des contenus fournisseurs et des articles de vulgarisation sur ce type de produit. <\/p>","width":"fit-content","max_width":"none","alignment":"left","type_preset":"rte","font":"var(--font-body--family)","font_size":"1rem","line_height":"normal","letter_spacing":"normal","case":"none","wrap":"pretty","color":"var(--color-foreground)","background":false,"background_color":"#00000026","corner_radius":0,"padding-block-start":0,"padding-block-end":0,"padding-inline-start":0,"padding-inline-end":0},"blocks":{}}},"block_order":["logo_CrXWXU","text_mVPQHV","text_QDNkLK","text_UjL3BP","text_HeEhzN","text_kmX33q","text_qeKfx4","text_ejBDFi","text_kBc3rF","text_EArqjb","text_PK7paa"],"name":"t:names.rich_text_section","settings":{"content_direction":"column","vertical_on_mobile":true,"horizontal_alignment":"flex-start","vertical_alignment":"center","align_baseline":false,"horizontal_alignment_flex_direction_column":"flex-start","vertical_alignment_flex_direction_column":"center","gap":25,"section_width":"page-width","section_height":"small","section_height_custom":50,"color_scheme":"scheme-4495f5b4-3089-429a-bda7-5d6c596aab40","background_media":"none","video_position":"cover","background_image_position":"cover","border":"none","border_width":1,"border_opacity":100,"border_radius":0,"toggle_overlay":false,"overlay_color":"#00000026","overlay_style":"solid","gradient_direction":"to top","padding-block-start":48,"padding-block-end":48}},"1777472202393b32f8":{"type":"_blocks","blocks":{"ai_gen_block_c98f4d2_4Ntf9U":{"type":"ai_gen_block_c98f4d2","settings":{"main_title":"Conseils d'utilisation","intro_text":"<p>Pour que Serenimo soit bien vécu par ton chien, l'idéal est de l'introduire progressivement et dans un moment calme. Comme pour tout nouvel accessoire, une approche douce donne souvent de meilleurs résultats.<\/p>","title_alignment":"left","tip_1_title":"Présente Serenimo dans un moment calme","tip_1_content":"<p>La première fois, fais découvrir le gilet à ton chien lorsqu'il est détendu, à la maison, sans source de stress autour de lui.<\/p>","tip_2_title":"Associe-le à quelque chose de positif","tip_2_content":"<p>Tu peux l'encourager avec une friandise, une caresse ou une voix rassurante pour créer une association positive dès le départ.<\/p>","tip_3_title":"Mets-le quelques minutes au début","tip_3_content":"<p>Commence par de courtes périodes, puis augmente progressivement le temps de port pour que ton chien s'y habitue confortablement.<\/p>","tip_4_title":"Utilise-le avant le moment sensible","tip_4_content":"<p>Pour une utilisation optimale, mets Serenimo quelques minutes avant la situation stressante :<\/p><ul><li>avant de partir de la maison<\/li><li>avant un trajet<\/li><li>avant une visite chez le vétérinaire<\/li><li>avant un orage ou des feux d'artifice<\/li><li>avant un changement d'habitude ou une situation inhabituelle<\/li><\/ul>","tip_5_title":"Vérifie qu'il est bien ajusté","tip_5_content":"<p>Le gilet doit être confortable, bien en place et non gênant. Il doit offrir un maintien doux tout en laissant à ton chien une bonne liberté de mouvement.<\/p>","tip_6_title":"Observe les réactions de ton chien","tip_6_content":"<p>Chaque chien est différent. Certains s'y habituent très vite, d'autres ont besoin d'un peu plus de temps. L'essentiel est d'intégrer Serenimo à la routine de manière progressive et rassurante.<\/p>","note_title":"Bon à savoir","note_text":"<p>Serenimo a été pensé comme une aide douce et simple à intégrer au quotidien. Il accompagne ton chien dans les moments sensibles, sans compliquer ta routine.<\/p>","desktop_width_percent":100,"section_padding":40,"border_radius":8,"title_spacing":30,"subtitle_spacing":15,"list_spacing":30,"item_spacing":20,"note_spacing":40,"item_padding":20,"item_border_radius":8,"item_border_width":4,"number_size":32,"number_font_size":16,"note_padding":20,"note_border_radius":8,"title_size":32,"item_title_size":18,"text_size":16,"note_title_size":18,"background_color":"#f5f1e8","title_color":"#5f7c8a","text_color":"#3e4347","item_background":"#fcfbf8","item_title_color":"#5f7c8a","accent_color":"#d9895b","number_text_color":"#ffffff","note_background":"#fcfbf8","note_border_color":"#a8bfa84d","note_title_color":"#d9895b"},"blocks":{}}},"block_order":["ai_gen_block_c98f4d2_4Ntf9U"],"settings":{"content_direction":"column","vertical_on_mobile":true,"horizontal_alignment":"flex-start","vertical_alignment":"center","align_baseline":false,"horizontal_alignment_flex_direction_column":"flex-start","vertical_alignment_flex_direction_column":"center","gap":12,"section_width":"page-width","section_height":"","section_height_custom":50,"color_scheme":"scheme-4495f5b4-3089-429a-bda7-5d6c596aab40","background_media":"none","video_position":"cover","background_image_position":"cover","border":"none","border_width":1,"border_opacity":100,"border_radius":0,"toggle_overlay":false,"overlay_color":"#00000026","overlay_style":"solid","gradient_direction":"to top","padding-block-start":0,"padding-block-end":0}}},"order":["main","section_76BTfJ","1777472202393b32f8"]}